Title: Trane Technologies Launches BrainBox AI Lab to Transform Energy Management and Sustainability in Buildings
Summary: Trane Technologies (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator, today announced the launch of the BrainBox AI Lab – igniting a new era in energy optimization for heating, ventilation, and air conditioning (HVAC) solutions in the built environment and refrigerated transport.
